do GlobalManager.play_animation.emit("disposable_worker_close")
do wait(2)
Disposable_worker: Finally
Disposable_worker: Management gave us of a new robot employee
do GlobalManager.play_animation.emit("disposable_worker", "grin")
Disposable_worker: A vending machine

Disposable_worker: Moments like these are exactly why I tolerate my job

do GlobalManager.play_animation.emit("disposable_worker_close_to_idle")
do wait(GlobalManager.current_animation_length)
do GlobalManager.play_animation.emit("disposable_worker_idle")

Disposable_worker: [color=#1bffc2]One large coffee[/color]. With cream and chocolate sprinkles.
Disposable_worker: Oh and a latte art of a swan.

# set slot responses for (disposable worker 1)
